    <p>Tagged with <a href="http://dirk-kutscher.info/tag/icn/" rel="tag">ICN</a>, <a href="http://dirk-kutscher.info/tag/ietf-2/" rel="tag">ietf</a>, <a href="http://dirk-kutscher.info/tag/information-centric-networking/" rel="tag">information-centric networking</a>, <a href="http://dirk-kutscher.info/tag/uri/" rel="tag">URI</a></p></div>
