<h2 id="post-99"><a href="http://dirk-kutscher.info/publications/talks/talk-on-information-centric-networking-at-6th-giitg-kuvs-workshop-on-%e2%80%9cfuture-internet%e2%80%9d/" rel="bookmark">Talk on Information-Centric Networking at 6th GI/ITG KuVS Workshop on “Future Internet”</a></h2>
<p class="comments"><a href="http://dirk-kutscher.info/publications/talks/talk-on-information-centric-networking-at-6th-giitg-kuvs-workshop-on-%e2%80%9cfuture-internet%e2%80%9d/#comments">without comments</a></p>

