	<p>I gave a talk on Information-Centric Networking at the <a href="http://www.ikt.uni-hannover.de/fg_future_internet.html">6th GI/ITG KuVS Workshop on “Future Internet”</a>.</p>
<p>[<a href="http://dl.dropbox.com/u/12009126/pub/FG_FI06_1.pdf">Abstract</a>][<a href="http://dl.dropbox.com/u/12009126/pub/FG_FI06_1p.pdf">Slide presentation</a>]</p>
